abstract: Pitcher Brady Aiken, who did not sign with Houston Astros after being picked first in draft, undergoes Tommy John Surgery.
lead_paragraph: Brady Aiken, the 18-year-old left-hander who did not sign after being last year’s No. 1 draft pick by the Houston Astros, had Tommy John surgery, he said in a statement on the Players’ Tribune website.

headline.main: Brady Aiken Has Tommy John Surgery
headline.print_headline: Baseball; No. 1 Pick Has Tommy John Surgery
